   Thangthat tuah u, Cungnungbik Bawi
   Cungnungbik Bawi, thangthat tuah u
   Zumh awk tlak, Pathian asi,
   Zung-zal in thangthat u.
   ( ZUNG-ZAL IN, THANGTHAT U ) 3

[V2]
 Pathian thangthat tuah u, Sermi vialte hna
 Nan sining, te cio in, Thangthat cio tuah u,
 Pathian thangthat tuah u, Sermi vialte hna
 Nan sining, te cio in, Thangthat cio tuah u.</lyrics>
